{{Quote|AT-STs will no longer be deployed on planets with an abundance of trees or other known obstacles such as rock-wielding primitives.|Imperial AT-ST Manual, updated shortly after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]|<ref name="The New Essential Guide to Vehicles and Vessels">''[[The New Essential Guide to Vehicles and Vessels]]''</ref>}}
The '''Imperial AT-ST manual''' was a manual written by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] to guide the reader on the aspects of an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[All Terrain Scout Transport/Legends|AT-ST]].

It was updated sometime after [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]], to inform that AT-STs would no longer be used on [[Planet/Legends|planets]] such as [[Endor/Legends|Endor]], alluding to the fact that many AT-STs were destroyed because of dangers on Endor.

